'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4122] on 4 June 2001 at 12:43:02 am'!"Change Set:		ButtonFillStyles-arDate:			4 June 2001Author:			Andreas RaabEnable the use of fill styles in buttons."!!FillStyle methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ar 6/4/2001 00:41'!mixed: fraction with: aColor	^self asColor mixed: fraction with: aColor! !!GradientFillStyle methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'ar 6/4/2001 00:42'!mixed: fraction with: aColor	^self copy colorRamp: (colorRamp collect:[:assoc| assoc key -> (assoc value mixed: fraction with: aColor)])! !!Morph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 6/4/2001 00:39'!color: aColor	color isColor ifFalse:[^self fillStyle: aColor].	color = aColor ifFalse: [		self removeProperty: #fillStyle.		color _ aColor.		self changed].! !!SimpleButtonMorph methodsFor: 'events' stamp: 'ar 6/4/2001 00:39'!mouseDown: evt	| now dt |	now _ Time millisecondClockValue.	oldColor _ self fillStyle. 	actWhen == #buttonDown		ifTrue: [self doButtonAction]		ifFalse: [	self updateVisualState: evt; refreshWorld].	dt _ Time millisecondClockValue - now max: 0.  "Time it took to do"	dt < 200 ifTrue: [(Delay forMilliseconds: 200-dt) wait].	self mouseStillDown: evt.! !!ChatButtonMorph methodsFor: 'events' stamp: 'ar 6/4/2001 00:40'!mouseDown: evt	oldColor _ self fillStyle.	self label: labelDown.	self doButtonDownAction.! !!SimpleSwitchMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'ar 6/4/2001 00:39'!mouseDown: evt	oldColor _ self fillStyle.! !